OL,4,CParminder Nagra: TV show turned me down
OL,5,Cfor being of Indian descent
OL,6, British-Asian actress Parminder Nagra
OL,7, has said she was once turned down for a
OL,8, role on a well-known US TV show because
OL,9, they "already had an Indian person".
OL,11,FShe told a podcast she had also heard
OL,12,Fproducers on an unnamed production say
OL,13,F"too many brown people" would not sell.
OL,15,FNagra made her name in the 2002 UK film
OL,16,FBend It Like Beckham before appearing
OL,17,Fthe American medical drama series ER.
OL,19,FWhile noting how on-screen diversity
OL,20,Fhad improved, she said she hoped it was
OL,21,Fnot just a quota-filling exercise.
